# OPTIONAL — only needed for the audio-memo feature.
# The core Board (debate -> written memo) needs NOTHING here.
#
# To enable the "listen on a walk" MP3 of each memo's short summary:
#   1. Get a free ElevenLabs API key at https://elevenlabs.io  (free tier = 10,000 chars/month)
#   2. Copy this file to ".env"   (cp .env.example .env)
#   3. Paste your key after the = below.
#   4. The .env file is gitignored — your key never gets committed.

ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
